Provide sample data

If real Natural Earth files are not included, generate a tiny sample dataset in code for:
	•	6 countries in Europe (polygons simplified rectangles acceptable)
	•	6 capitals (points)
	•	3 rivers (lines)
So the app runs out-of-the-box. Make it easy to swap in real Natural Earth GeoJSON later.

⸻

Quality Bar
	•	App should be fast: lazy-load data per pack
	•	Clean UI, kid-friendly, readable fonts, large tap targets
	•	No external API keys
	•	Everything works as static files on GitHub Pages

Definition of done
	•	All required files in the requested structure exist and are wired.
	•	README includes exact local run, data rebuild, and deploy steps.
	•	Sample data allows out-of-the-box demo without external downloads.
	•	No runtime errors in production build and no broken controls in mobile layout.
